Package de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.ui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MainApplication
    Instances of this class are the main application of RyCON.
    RyCONLauncher
    RyCONLauncher controls the launch process of RyCON and initialize the Display, a SplashScreen and all of it's services before the main window is shown.
    SplashScreen
    SplashScreen displays a splash screen while RyCON is starting.
    UpdateDialog
    UpdateDialog implements an update dialog for RyCON.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Images
    The Images enumeration holds the paths to all used icons or images of RyCON.
    MainApplicationDnDButtons
    This enumeration is used for the drag'n drop enabled widgets buttons of the MainApplication.
    Sizes
    The Sizes enumeration holds all the default size values for the gui of RyCON.
